(23, '<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">GUIDELINES FOR WRITING INTERNSHIP REPORT<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">This document has been designed to guide students of the Department of Computer<br />Engineering on writing their internship reports. All students are required to strictly respect<br />these guidelines and format prescribed for their internship reports.<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">General overview updated<br /></span></p>\r\n<table class=\"NormalTable\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"306\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Paper </span></td>\r\n<td width=\"307\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">A4 size paper should be used</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"306\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Font </span></td>\r\n<td width=\"307\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Font should be Times New Roman, size 12 for<br />body of report and size 16 for titles</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"306\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Margin </span></td>\r\n<td width=\"307\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Use 2.5cm for left and right margins, 2cm for top<br />and bottom margins</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"306\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Spacing </span></td>\r\n<td width=\"307\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">1.5 line spacing should be used for the body</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"306\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Language </span></td>\r\n<td width=\"307\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Use Standard Formal level of English only</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"306\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Page Limit </span></td>\r\n<td width=\"307\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">The number of pages limit is 20&plusmn; 5 excluding<br />the preliminary pages</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"306\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Justification </span></td>\r\n<td width=\"307\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">The whole document should be fully (left and<br />right) justified</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"306\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Page Numbering</span></td>\r\n<td width=\"307\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">All pages should be numbered. Preliminary pages<br />should be given Roman numbers (i, ii, iii, etc)<br />while the others have numerical numbers,<br />starting with 1 from the first page of chapter 1.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"306\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Paragraphs and Sections</span></td>\r\n<td width=\"307\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Insert a line break before and after every section<br />and subsection. Paragraphs should be justified<br />and separated by a blank line.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"306\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Heading and Subheadings </span></td>\r\n<td width=\"307\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Headings and subheadings should be numbered<br />and well formatted</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"306\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Punctuations, Spelling and Grammar Check </span></td>\r\n<td width=\"307\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Use correct punctuation marks. Spelling and<br />grammar should be accurate</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">NB</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">: The typed pages should be in spiral binding in black and white color. A hard and soft<br />copy should be submitted to the department of Computer Engineering.<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Format and Contents of the report<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">The report should have the following format which comprises some preliminary pages (Title</span><br /><span class=\"fontstyle3\">University of Buea (UB) Faculty of Engineering and Technology (FET)<br />Department of Computer Engineering </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">3<br />page, Table of Contents, Dedication, and Acknowledgement) as well as some<br />chapters/sections.</span> </p>', '<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Details of some elements in the structure of report are as follow:<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Title Page<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Contains title (including subtitle), name of the University and Faculty, with UB logo,<br />name of the company where you did internship, student name and registration<br />number/matricule, technical and academic supervisor(s), their institutions and email<br />addresses<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Table of Contents<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Should contain list all headings and subheadings with page numbers, indent<br />subheadings.<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Dedication<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">This section contains person or group of persons in whose honour the report is written.<br />(This is optional and can be left out)<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Acknowledgement<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">In this section you acknowledge the assistance and support of the people who helped<br />you in the completion of your internship and internship report.<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">List of Tables<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">List page numbers of all tables. The list should include a short title for each table but<br />not the whole caption<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">List of Figures<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">List page numbers of all figures. The list should include a short title for each table but<br />not the whole caption</span> </p>', 11, 1, 0, NULL, '2019-02-19 14:12:49', '2019-02-19 14:12:49');
