&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"mso-list: l1 level2 lfo1;\"><a name=\"_Toc3332591\"></a><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: \'Arial Narrow\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Arial Narrow\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.2<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\">Constraints</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"StyleInfoBlueArialLeftLeft0After12pt\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a name=\"_Toc294191293\"></a><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; color: windowtext; font-style: normal; mso-bidi-font-style: italic;\">Some constraint/limitation realized:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"StyleInfoBlueArialLeftLeft0After12pt\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><span style=\"mso-bookmark: _Toc294191293;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">a)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\">change of the system outline from whole text to a one that can be ticked</span></span><span style=\"mso-bookmark: _Toc294191293;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; color: windowtext;\">. This has not yet been fully implemented as it required some ajax mechanism and due to time constraints.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"StyleInfoBlueArialLeftLeft0After12pt\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><span style=\"mso-bookmark: _Toc294191293;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">b)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--